englishTranslationText:
They	 ask	 you	 regarding	 the	 mountains;	
proclaim,	 “My	 Lord	will	 blow	 them	into	
bits	and	scatter	them.”

So	they	both	ate	from	it	- thereupon	their	
shame	became	manifest	to	them,	and	they	started	applying	on	themselves	the	leaves	of	heaven;	
and	Adam	lapsed	in	obeying	his	Lord,	so	did	not	reach	his	goal.	(Of	achieving	immortality)
